][vc_accordion_tab title="If I cancel and then decide to rejoin, do I have to pay another joining fee?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540790342516{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"] If you rejoin within 30 days of cancelling we will waive your joining fee. However, if you rejoin after that 30-day period you would have to pay another joining fee. Management may make exceptions for those who cancel for health issues or military deployment.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="What if I decide to cancel? Are there any cancellation fees?"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1540790379129{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}"]Memberships where a joining fee was paid may be cancelled at any time by filling out a cancellation form at any 10 Fitness location at least three business days before the draft date and paying any past due balance.

